Read AGENTS.md before every action. Read manifest.yaml before creating any file.
Never install dependencies not in manifest.yaml.
SQLite, Ollama, RAG, and backend AI are permanently banned.
Edit existing files. Never create variants (_fixed, _v2, _clean, etc).
